oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Apollo 12 - Moon travel tapes - Tape 3 Side 1 PT. 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tape 3 (Side 1) [Part 1] of an unknown number of tapes. Program sent on the Apollo 12 space mission for astronaut's enjoyment. Originally from a cassette Tape. Featuring Bob Wills, Charley Pride, Redd Stewart, Pee Wee King, Faron Young, Po Boys, Conway Twitty, Charlie Pride, Roger Miller, Ernest Tubb, Jerry Lee Lewis, Buddy Spicher, David Houston, and Dan Gibson.
